misc: armchina-npu: update to cix_opensource driver ABI

Refresh the Sky1 NPU driver from cixtech/cix_opensource__npu_driver
cix_mainline_upstream_dev commit 047b23e91665008ae7865690da7a3c01dc573af7.
This is an ABI migration to the current CIX userspace interface.

